Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:01:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a little treat for you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of ours has prepared sort of a slide presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of what our life is like on the ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So a lot of the pictures that you're going to see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,were taken of our personal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the bookstore, if you purchase $100,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you get this video free.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So we wanted to give that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful, and I think you're really going to enjoy it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and get out the Kleenex.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:20:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For all of you that aren't familiar with our work
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and our first-time comers, this is our ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And we did a whole series on that in 2002.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is our little ego that we carry around with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And we don't oppose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We just embrace it and love it and know that it's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is what the teddy bear represents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be somebody out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sing-song kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh, keen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned this from my father 80 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keem, oh, kind, oh, dar, oh, ah, many, I, many, oh, many, rum,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,stum, fum, me, diddle, soup, peck, fetty, won't you lick them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,mick them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:21:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keem, oh, kind, oh, dar, oh, ah, many, I, many, oh, many, rum,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,stum, fum, me, diddle, soup, peck, fetty, won't you lick them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,mick them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the love I got from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'd say, say it slow, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I memorized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was love 80 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Keem, oh, kind, oh, dar, oh, ah, many, I, many, oh, many,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,rum, stum, fum, me, diddle, soup, peck, fetty, won't you lick
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,them, mick them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:23:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is willing, but the body is tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to say goodbye to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.51,0:23:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We will carry you in our hearts and in our prayers and hope
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.43,0:23:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that we meet again in the hereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we're going to start the lecture at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.05,0:23:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fran will read the slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctors, eyesight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't very good anymore, and so he can no longer read the slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've asked someone to read the slides for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And, uh, we are going to go continue with the lecture and, um, bless you all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:24:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for coming such a long way to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.33,0:24:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.81,0:24:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't take snuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.92,0:24:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Our love for you is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.75,0:24:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.24,0:24:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the next honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.54,0:24:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to start the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.69,0:24:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.00,0:24:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A logarithmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.13,0:25:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Scale from one to 1000 where courage is the critical factor point of integrity at 200 below which all the energies are negative and above which all the energies are positive love calibrates 500 and over unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.92,0:25:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.25,0:25:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.66,0:25:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Next slide, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.28,0:25:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.30,0:25:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Distribution of the levels of consciousness shown in a pyramid showing that 85% of the world's population calibrates below the level of integrity at 200 and at the top of the pyramid, 15% calibrate above 200, which is the level of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.79,0:25:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,An integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.57,0:26:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Distribution of the levels of consciousness shown.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.92,0:26:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And a fulcrum where the 15% of the world's population that calibrate in integrity over level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.64,0:26:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Counterbalance the 85% of the world's population that calibrate negatively or below level 200 of courage and integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.75,0:26:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And then 20% of the world's population that calibrate negatively or below level 200 of courage and integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.24,0:26:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Exaggerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.74,0:26:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have the animal kingdom. I'll mention some of Doc's favorites. Bacteria 1. Octopus 20. The Komodo dragon at 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.32,0:27:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And at level 200 in the animal kingdom, we reach the grazers, those who do not kill as a means to survive. So the zebra, the gazelle, the giraffe, the deer, the elk, and the family dog at 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.20,0:27:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have certain exceptions, such as the kitty's purr at the level of love, 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.33,0:27:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And the doggie's wagging tail at 500. The level of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.20,0:27:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see from this next chart that as consciousness level moves up and rises in the map of consciousness, rate of unemployment decreases, rate of poverty decreases, happiness increases, and rate of criminality decreases.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.89,0:27:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So for example, at the level of 50, which is apathy and below.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.25,0:28:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,97% of people are unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.25,0:28:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,65% are in poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.25,0:28:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,0% are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.25,0:28:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And 98% criminality.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.92,0:28:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,However, by level 200, which is the critical point of integrity, where the valence of the energy shifts to positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.92,0:28:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only 8% unemployment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.92,0:28:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,1.5% poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.92,0:28:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,40% happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.92,0:28:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And 9.0% criminality.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.14,0:28:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At the level of love, 5 to 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.29,0:28:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Unemployment is 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.29,0:28:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Poverty 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.29,0:28:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness, 98%.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.54,0:29:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Correlation of the levels of consciousness and the rate of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.54,0:29:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At consciousness level shame, at the bottom of the map of consciousness, only 1% of people are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.54,0:29:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By the level courage, 255% of people are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.54,0:29:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,At the level acceptance, which is logarithm 350, 71% of people are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.77,0:29:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,At level 500, 89% are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.13,0:29:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the time of joy, which is 540 to 599, 99% of people are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.13,0:29:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,99% of people are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.13,0:29:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we have one of the doctor's favorite slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.94,0:29:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The wolf in sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.77,0:30:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are not always as they appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.71,0:30:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrations of the great avatars and spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.90,0:30:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ, 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.64,0:30:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha, 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.22,0:30:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoroaster, 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.53,0:30:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The 12 Christian apostles, 980.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.53,0:30:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of God as Om, 975.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.73,0:30:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,John the Baptist, 930.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.95,0:30:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Moses, 910.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.21,0:30:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Abraham, 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.55,0:30:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Paul, 740.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.55,0:30:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual teachers in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.26,0:31:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.26,0:31:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These are historical examples.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.29,0:31:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Lawrence, 575.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.33,0:31:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Father Pio, 585.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.42,0:31:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Confucius, 590.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.04,0:31:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumi, 550.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.20,0:31:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus, 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.25,0:31:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dilgo Khyentse Rinpoche, 575.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.90,0:31:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Swami Prabhavananda, 550.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.31,0:31:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.81,0:31:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is the ultimate law of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.81,0:31:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This statement calibrates 750.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.81,0:31:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Love God with all thy heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.16,0:32:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,all thy soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.16,0:32:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and all thy mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.16,0:32:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Love thy neighbor as thyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.16,0:32:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Love makes the world go round.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.85,0:32:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a many-splendored thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.85,0:32:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.85,0:32:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a way to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.53,0:32:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Love facilitates healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.53,0:32:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the famous duck story.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.92,0:32:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.92,0:32:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.92,0:32:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Love God with all your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.92,0:32:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and all your soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.18,0:32:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what does that mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.91,0:32:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.91,0:32:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.91,0:32:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Love God with all your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.91,0:32:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and all your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.91,0:32:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and all your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.91,0:32:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we apply that to everyday living?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.46,0:32:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You become that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.49,0:32:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And then everything happens
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.53,0:32:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,appropriately,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.53,0:32:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.05,0:32:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,due to what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.29,0:32:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you approach a group of people
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.22,0:33:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and the love of God
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.67,0:33:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is what motivates you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.67,0:33:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,all the people in the crowd go,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.67,0:33:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How do they go, folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.13,0:33:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.60,0:33:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's telling them, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.39,0:33:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll show the devil where the hell to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.68,0:33:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Love God with all your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.09,0:33:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.09,0:33:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will be wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.25,0:33:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to your fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.25,0:33:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And love thy neighbor
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.18,0:33:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,as thyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.47,0:33:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you interpret that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.81,0:33:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to interpret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.81,0:33:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You become that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.01,0:33:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As you become loving,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.01,0:33:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it's your way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.01,0:33:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So lovingness to me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.01,0:33:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is a way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.07,0:33:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.07,0:33:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.07,0:33:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, how can I be
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.71,0:33:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of help to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.71,0:34:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I comfort you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.71,0:34:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I loan you some money when you're broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.71,0:34:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I help you find a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.86,0:34:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I console you when you've
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.86,0:34:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,suffered a major loss in your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.86,0:34:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovingness is a way of being
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.86,0:34:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.86,0:34:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And that way you light up the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.36,0:34:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is the way
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.36,0:34:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.51,0:34:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.09,0:34:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we apply that to our everyday life?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.09,0:34:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.82,0:34:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.82,0:34:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.82,0:34:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because that's what you become?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.82,0:34:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you become.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.82,0:34:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you become loving,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.09,0:34:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you radiate the energy of God
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.09,0:34:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.57,0:34:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are a blessing to be in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.57,0:34:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and other people are like a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.30,0:35:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.57,0:35:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And love
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.30,0:35:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,facilitates healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.30,0:35:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.30,0:35:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Love facilitates healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.44,0:35:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.44,0:35:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Love facilitates healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.50,0:35:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The more loving you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.17,0:35:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to love all my patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.17,0:35:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.69,0:35:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I loved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.03,0:35:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I used to have a patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.03,0:35:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,he had a picture of me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.03,0:35:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and he would go home and he'd put my picture
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.03,0:35:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,on the wall and he would say when he feels
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.03,0:35:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,bad he looked at the picture and feels better.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.03,0:35:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So that gave me the hint
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.03,0:35:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that love heals.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.03,0:35:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And so as a physician
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.30,0:35:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved all my patients
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.61,0:35:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.90,0:35:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Might make them nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.46,0:35:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So as a physician
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.46,0:36:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,then you sent love
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.46,0:36:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to the patients you were treating.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.46,0:36:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved all the patients that I treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.46,0:36:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you were such a success
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.46,0:36:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,as a psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.46,0:36:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because you were sending them love
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.46,0:36:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and thinking about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.92,0:36:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the biggest psychiatric practice
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.92,0:36:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.92,0:36:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for 25 years or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.07,0:36:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We treated a thousand patients
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.07,0:36:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a year. A thousand patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.07,0:36:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I loved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.26,0:36:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So if physicians
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.26,0:36:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,would say a prayer for their patients
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.26,0:36:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to get better then that would help them
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.26,0:36:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,recuperate
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.26,0:36:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.26,0:36:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I prayed over all of them but I didn't tell them I was doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.26,0:36:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It might make them nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.94,0:36:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We have up here the duck story.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.94,0:36:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us the duck story?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.94,0:36:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,About the hunter who
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.94,0:36:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer would hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.94,0:36:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh it makes me cry to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.94,0:36:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can tell it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.01,0:36:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway it's a relatively
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.01,0:36:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,well known story now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.01,0:37:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy hunted ducks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.01,0:37:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a duck hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.01,0:37:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a normal everyday duck hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.80,0:37:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To me it seems like
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.80,0:37:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,an abomination to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.80,0:37:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He went duck hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.80,0:37:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And he shot this duck
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.80,0:37:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.26,0:37:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the duck wasn't killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.28,0:37:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it was
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.28,0:37:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,badly injured and the duck
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.28,0:37:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,fell to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.32,0:37:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And after this duck fell
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.73,0:37:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to the ground it's mate
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.73,0:37:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it's female mate
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.73,0:37:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,flew down on top
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.17,0:37:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of the injured duck and she put her
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.98,0:38:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,she put her wings over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.61,0:38:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After that he never killed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.61,0:38:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,another duck. Okay we'll go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.63,0:38:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.82,0:38:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.28,0:38:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.63,0:38:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.46,0:38:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,within his own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.76,0:38:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And he gave up hunting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.76,0:38:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,as a sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.21,0:39:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But the female duck
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.69,0:39:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,fell on top of the male
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.07,0:39:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,duck and she
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.09,0:39:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,shelled her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.80,0:39:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And he never hunted again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.80,0:39:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So love has a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.01,0:39:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,transformative power.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.01,0:39:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you become loving
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.61,0:39:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there are certain things
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.86,0:39:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you can never do again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.23,0:39:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can also perform the miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.23,0:39:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,without labeling
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.67,0:39:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.28,0:39:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do things other people cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.28,0:39:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And people will do things
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.34,0:39:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for you they would not do for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.34,0:39:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So love has a very
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.73,0:39:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,powerful transformative effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.73,0:39:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best not to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.46,0:40:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people that you love them
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.46,0:40:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because they'll get scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.46,0:40:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll think you have
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.48,0:40:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,designs on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.44,0:40:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So loving this is a way
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.44,0:40:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of being. It's a way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.44,0:40:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And it transforms
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.61,0:40:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,everything around you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.01,0:40:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the radiation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.01,0:40:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of that energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.71,0:40:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,People that are hateful
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.71,0:40:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in your presence will suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.71,0:40:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,become willing to forgive others.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.03,0:40:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll say
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.03,0:40:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,if you go back over that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.03,0:40:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,how would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.03,0:40:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can see the person
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.13,0:40:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,transform right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.13,0:40:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And they'd say well I wouldn't have been
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.13,0:40:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,too young to know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.28,0:40:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They would find an excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.28,0:40:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to defend the person instead of attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.28,0:40:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So we become defenders
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.76,0:40:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of love and life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.76,0:40:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And we stop being
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.76,0:40:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,attackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.76,0:41:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.17,0:41:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was glad during World War II
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.50,0:41:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have to kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.50,0:41:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to maintain this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.84,0:41:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a bosun's mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.55,0:41:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I brought the ship through
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.51,0:41:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.61,0:41:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,storms.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.34,0:41:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship went over 90 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.34,0:41:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was standing on the bulkhead
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.34,0:41:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with one foot
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.34,0:41:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,on the bulkhead and the other
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.34,0:41:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,at the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.69,0:41:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I stayed at the wheel for 12 hours non-stop
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.69,0:41:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because everybody else was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.69,0:41:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody was terribly seasick
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.78,0:41:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and laying on the floor throwing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.78,0:41:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I just stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.61,0:41:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,at the wheel
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.84,0:41:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess 12 or 20
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.61,0:41:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how many hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.61,0:41:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a long couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.48,0:41:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So love empowers us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.48,0:41:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It allows you to steer a ship for
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.48,0:41:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,close to a whole day without food
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.51,0:42:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or drink or
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.73,0:42:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.73,0:42:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have had water or something
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.73,0:42:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.34,0:42:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So love empowers us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.34,0:42:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.84,0:42:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and love is
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.03,0:42:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.65,0:42:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And we also have to forgive ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.65,0:42:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for our trespasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.65,0:42:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgive myself for the errors
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.65,0:42:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have made, oh Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.65,0:42:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was less evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.23,0:42:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.23,0:42:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Love calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.42,0:42:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,500 and over
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.42,0:42:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,on the map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.42,0:42:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart chakra
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.42,0:42:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates 505.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.42,0:42:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagpipes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.90,0:42:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,are an example
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.90,0:42:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of the energy of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.90,0:42:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's love of pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.90,0:42:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.90,0:43:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Romantic love.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.01,0:43:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Loveless
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.32,0:43:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,equals flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.32,0:43:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.73,0:43:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The golden rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.73,0:43:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do unto others
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.73,0:43:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as you would have them
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.73,0:43:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,do unto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.73,0:43:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of attributes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.65,0:43:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Love increases
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.86,0:43:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,perceived value.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.86,0:43:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Love increases
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.86,0:43:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.30,0:43:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.46,0:43:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,agape,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.46,0:43:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which is universal love,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.46,0:43:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.46,0:43:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,570.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.46,0:43:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Love
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.67,0:43:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.71,0:43:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.73,0:43:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.73,0:43:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I love doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.73,0:43:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.34,0:43:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.63,0:43:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.63,0:44:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.21,0:44:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, in this last
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.21,0:44:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,slide, you have given
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.21,0:44:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,several examples of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.21,0:44:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, different types of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.21,0:44:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Like
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.34,0:44:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,enthusiasm,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.34,0:44:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the forgiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.34,0:44:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.34,0:44:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So each one of these is an
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.34,0:44:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,aspect of love, yet
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.34,0:44:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in a different form.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.59,0:44:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.59,0:44:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the last thing I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.59,0:44:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But in a different form.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.59,0:44:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Different forms of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.59,0:44:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all different forms of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.59,0:44:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can encourage your
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.59,0:44:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,fellow, you know, to make life better
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.50,0:44:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,for everybody around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.78,0:44:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's always been my ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.78,0:44:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To make things go better,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.03,0:44:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,or the eggs got fried better,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.09,0:44:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,or the duckies got saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.09,0:44:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or the kitty got fed this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.19,0:44:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we left the house
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.36,0:44:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.36,0:44:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it was very important to make sure the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.36,0:45:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,kitties had enough food.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.51,0:45:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So we had three kitties all lined up,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.51,0:45:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for their breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.51,0:45:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And before we left,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.94,0:45:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,we had to make sure the doggie
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.94,0:45:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,had enough food and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.98,0:45:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So to share your love with
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.98,0:45:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,everything around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.98,0:45:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,kitties and doggies,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.98,0:45:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.53,0:45:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and even villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.80,0:45:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A captured villain,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.80,0:45:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it's up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.09,0:45:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to make his life tolerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.09,0:45:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, I'm sorry that I have to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.09,0:45:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,hold a gun to your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.09,0:45:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.17,0:45:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.17,0:45:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.76,0:45:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as motivator.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.76,0:45:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Love
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.65,0:45:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.65,0:45:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.65,0:46:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.01,0:46:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.01,0:46:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.75,0:46:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.38,0:46:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as essence
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.38,0:46:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.21,0:46:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as group
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.21,0:46:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.53,0:46:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Example.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.69,0:46:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcoholics Anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.69,0:46:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,540.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.69,0:46:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of unconditional
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.69,0:46:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,love.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.69,0:46:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I want you to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.13,0:46:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,explain to everyone here
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.13,0:46:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the difference between
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.13,0:46:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,love at 500
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.13,0:46:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.13,0:46:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.57,0:46:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that it's that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.57,0:46:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to differentiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.57,0:46:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,At 540,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.19,0:46:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you love everybody and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.19,0:46:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.53,0:46:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,even Adolf Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.82,0:46:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at him as a person
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.82,0:46:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,who was taken over
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.96,0:47:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,by negative energies.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.38,0:47:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're willing to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.38,0:47:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,forgive Adolf Hitler
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.92,0:47:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who couldn't help what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.92,0:47:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to him. That he was
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.26,0:47:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,overcome by evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.69,0:47:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of hating evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.69,0:47:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel sorry that people have
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.69,0:47:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,become overwhelmed by evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.69,0:47:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.94,0:47:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolf did what
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.94,0:47:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,he thought he was required
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.94,0:47:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to do by honor
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.94,0:47:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and in its
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.48,0:47:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,contextualization at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.90,0:47:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can love even Adolf Hitler
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.90,0:47:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in unconditional love,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.32,0:47:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you would be able to forgive him
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.32,0:47:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and accept him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.34,0:47:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd forgive even Hitler, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.34,0:47:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he was captured by certain
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.34,0:47:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ideals. Captured by
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.34,0:47:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the thinginess of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.34,0:47:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.34,0:47:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.34,0:47:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,who violates the law of love
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.34,0:47:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is really a victim of
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.34,0:48:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,some other
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.46,0:48:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,societal belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.46,0:48:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or the pressures of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.59,0:48:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,During the World War
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.07,0:48:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,II, I didn't hate the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.07,0:48:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.13,0:48:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pearl Harbor, I didn't hate
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.13,0:48:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.50,0:48:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hate anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.42,0:48:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.42,0:48:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you still had to conduct yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.57,0:48:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but without hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.00,0:48:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it out of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.00,0:48:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a sense of duty and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.00,0:48:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,loyalty to your fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.00,0:48:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The people on the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.76,0:48:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the only way they got through the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.76,0:48:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okinawa Typhoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.76,0:48:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,turned over something like
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.82,0:48:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,90 ships. 90 ships went down
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.82,0:48:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Okinawa Typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.05,0:48:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was at the wheel the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.05,0:48:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was just thankful
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.73,0:48:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that, Lord, I could
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.73,0:48:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,sustain
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.73,0:48:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the life. Everybody was seasick.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.73,0:49:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all laying on the deck. It was pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.82,0:49:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody laying on the deck throwing up
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.82,0:49:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for days. It was really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.11,0:49:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And so steering the ship was up
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.11,0:49:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to me because I was
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.11,0:49:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the only one, apparently, that wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.11,0:49:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,seasick.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.11,0:49:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But we hit 90 degrees because
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.59,0:49:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember I was standing on the bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.98,0:49:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing up straight on the bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.98,0:49:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So we were over 90 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.34,0:49:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So we serve our fellow man
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.34,0:49:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,out of a commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.46,0:49:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.19,0:49:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,our human nature
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.19,0:49:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as God would have us
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.30,0:49:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,understand it. We thank Thee,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.63,0:49:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,O Lord, for our life and we dedicate
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.63,0:49:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it to Thy service. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.63,0:49:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.90,0:49:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as admiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.90,0:49:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as respect
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.32,0:49:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as in love of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.32,0:49:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,country and countrymen
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.32,0:50:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.51,0:50:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as valor.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.71,0:50:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of shipmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.71,0:50:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.57,0:50:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.57,0:50:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraternal love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.05,0:50:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,as in buddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.21,0:50:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,classmates,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.21,0:50:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.21,0:50:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.94,0:50:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.94,0:50:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is letting
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.53,0:50:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,go of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.53,0:50:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry Jempolski's book.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.53,0:50:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.46,0:50:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.46,0:50:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.48,0:50:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as cherishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.32,0:50:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maternal love.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.32,0:50:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-sacrificing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.34,0:50:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.73,0:50:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as an existential
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.73,0:50:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,style.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.86,0:50:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This lecture is the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.86,0:50:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,result of love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.86,0:51:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.86,0:51:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was speaking to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.90,0:51:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,some ladies who were up front here
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.90,0:51:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,before the lecture started
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.90,0:51:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and we were talking
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.03,0:51:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,about what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.05,0:51:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to be wives and mothers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.05,0:51:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and how important it is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.05,0:51:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to each one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.05,0:51:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to hold that spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.05,0:51:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,torch
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.05,0:51:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in our family
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.05,0:51:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it's up to us
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.05,0:51:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep that spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.05,0:51:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,strong
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.05,0:51:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as women of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.05,0:51:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.05,0:51:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.05,0:51:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,pass that along to everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.05,0:51:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that we as women
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.05,0:51:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as wives
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.05,0:51:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and mothers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.05,0:51:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,need to inspire
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.13,0:51:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,our children and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.13,0:51:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,mates to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.13,0:51:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,take up that torch
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.13,0:51:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and follow God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.44,0:51:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.73,0:52:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Every morning
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.34,0:52:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks for your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.73,0:52:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Every night
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.07,0:52:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank God for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.07,0:52:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How animals
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.30,0:52:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,affect your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.23,0:52:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The songbird's song
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.23,0:52:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 500
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.23,0:52:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.42,0:52:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The kitty's purr
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.42,0:52:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 500
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.42,0:52:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.42,0:52:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The doggy's
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.42,0:52:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,wagging tail
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.42,0:52:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 500
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.42,0:52:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.42,0:52:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The family cat
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.42,0:53:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 245
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.42,0:53:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the family dog
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.61,0:53:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.61,0:53:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,at 250
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.61,0:53:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and having
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.98,0:53:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.98,0:53:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,increases your lifespan
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.98,0:53:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,by 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.98,0:53:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.55,0:53:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.09,0:53:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you own a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.26,0:53:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you will live 10 years
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.26,0:53:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.38,0:53:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think of all the idiotic
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.38,0:53:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,exercises, crazy diets
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.38,0:53:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,people go through,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.59,0:53:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you just buy a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.59,0:53:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and live 10 more years?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.59,0:53:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Save yourself all those horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.59,0:53:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,low cholesterol diets and crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.86,0:53:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to die of cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.86,0:53:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,poisoning when you're 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.21,0:53:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I'm over
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.21,0:53:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How old am I now? I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.21,0:53:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how old I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.38,0:54:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How old am I? 84.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.38,0:54:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.38,0:54:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well without a dog I would have been
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.38,0:54:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.38,0:54:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So Kelsey my doggy at home
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.76,0:54:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,who I love and adore.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.82,0:54:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kelsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.36,0:54:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Kelsey?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.13,0:54:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.19,0:54:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.19,0:54:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to the pound
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.19,0:54:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and adopted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.19,0:54:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave went in and
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.19,0:54:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,all these dogs are jumping around
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.19,0:54:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,pick me, pick me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.19,0:54:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and here she was just sitting in the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.19,0:54:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and he says I want that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.65,0:54:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And Gabe and I looked at each other like
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.65,0:54:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.65,0:54:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.65,0:54:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He goes no I want that dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.65,0:54:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And we came home with her and she has been a joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.94,0:54:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She herds the kitties.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.94,0:54:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All the other dogs jumped around.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.94,0:54:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kelsey just lay in the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.94,0:54:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.09,0:55:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.09,0:55:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So she got me through the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.15,0:55:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Love me, love my dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.63,0:55:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fact that owning a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.63,0:55:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,adds ten years to your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.63,0:55:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean that's just a major issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.63,0:55:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years is quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.63,0:55:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.30,0:55:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.01,0:55:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kelsey asked me to bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.01,0:55:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.21,0:55:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring it up Kelsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.21,0:55:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my promise to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.21,0:55:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.17,0:55:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in the level of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.15,0:55:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The statement
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.15,0:55:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,love is the ultimate law
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.15,0:55:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.15,0:55:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.15,0:55:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,750.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.11,0:55:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sat Chit Ananda
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.25,0:55:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.25,0:56:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Agape
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.34,0:56:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,taught by Jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.71,0:56:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.71,0:56:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,570.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.61,0:56:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan Boyle's
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.61,0:56:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,voice
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.84,0:56:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at 550.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.84,0:56:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.98,0:56:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.98,0:56:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,540.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.82,0:56:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The movie The Pacific
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.82,0:56:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.88,0:56:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,500.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.82,0:56:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.82,0:56:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at 430.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.82,0:56:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother's Day
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.07,0:56:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.07,0:56:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,300.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.53,0:56:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Solar plexus versus
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.53,0:56:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,love.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.76,0:56:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.63,0:56:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Attachment and
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.63,0:56:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ambitious craving
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.63,0:56:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,are from the solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.73,0:56:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Examples
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.73,0:57:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,love of wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.78,0:57:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.78,0:57:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.78,0:57:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of being right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.78,0:57:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of glamour.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.78,0:57:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.78,0:57:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of stardom.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.78,0:57:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of public attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.78,0:57:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Words that describe
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.01,0:57:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.01,0:57:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.01,0:57:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.01,0:57:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Heartfelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.01,0:57:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Join.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.01,0:57:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.01,0:57:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.01,0:57:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensual.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.01,0:57:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.01,0:57:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Protective.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.01,0:57:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.01,0:57:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Inclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.01,0:57:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.01,0:57:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.01,0:57:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Affectionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.01,0:57:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.01,0:57:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.01,0:57:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cordial.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.01,0:57:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.01,0:58:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Satisfying.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.01,0:58:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gracious.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.01,0:58:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.01,0:58:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.01,0:58:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uplifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.01,0:58:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Holistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.53,0:58:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetness.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.53,0:58:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a progressively
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.57,0:58:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,unconditional energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.57,0:58:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovingness is a way of being
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.30,0:58:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.30,0:58:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.30,0:58:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.03,0:58:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And supportive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.61,0:58:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Love emanates from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.61,0:58:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That first statement you said
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.61,0:58:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is that love is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.61,0:58:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,progressively
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.61,0:58:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,unconditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.61,0:58:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you love,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.61,0:58:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the more you can love.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.78,0:58:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one reason to have a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.01,0:58:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You live 10 years longer
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.01,0:58:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because it brings up
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.01,0:58:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of love
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.01,0:59:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the energy of love heals
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.01,0:59:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and prolongs life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.00,0:59:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're thankful for your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.00,0:59:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thankful to God
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.61,0:59:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,because of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.61,0:59:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.61,0:59:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank thee, O Lord, for my life
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.67,0:59:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the miracles of this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.92,0:59:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always thank God
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.92,0:59:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for our dog and our kitties.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.92,0:59:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I thank you for the dog
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.92,0:59:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the kitties.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.92,0:59:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because they represent love.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.98,0:59:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The kitties purr, purr, purr, purr, purr, purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.98,0:59:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a kitty that climbs on the bed
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.98,0:59:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as we're in bed
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.98,0:59:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it starts to go purr, purr, purr, purr, purr, purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.98,0:59:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So we surround
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.98,0:59:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ourselves with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.46,0:59:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.03,0:59:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always saying lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.03,0:59:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.03,0:59:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we apply that to our daily lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.09,0:59:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You just become,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.09,0:59:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you become that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.09,0:59:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you do and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.09,0:59:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,every movement,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.09,1:00:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then is energized by the lovingness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.09,1:00:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,which you own within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.65,1:00:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I say as I talk
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.65,1:00:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to this audience,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.65,1:00:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like an energy running out.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.65,1:00:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to share
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.65,1:00:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what I hold in my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.65,1:00:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,as a knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.65,1:00:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.38,1:00:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hold it in my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.38,1:00:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of them
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.38,1:00:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that they should all be feeling it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.53,1:00:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray for the inner experience
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.53,1:00:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of divine love
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.53,1:00:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for everyone here present now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.53,1:00:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, in the name of the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.65,1:00:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the Father, and the Son of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.65,1:00:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And love is forgiving, nurturing,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.75,1:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and supportive.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.75,1:00:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, as a woman you know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.26,1:00:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In our society we look to the woman
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.26,1:00:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as the representative
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.26,1:00:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of maternal love as the ideal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.73,1:01:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.01,1:01:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It emanates.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.01,1:01:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.01,1:01:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It emanates from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.01,1:01:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Love emanates from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.01,1:01:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God, is it emanating someplace here?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.01,1:01:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's emanating.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.01,1:01:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Folks help!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.01,1:01:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the emanator squad.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.11,1:01:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.11,1:01:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.11,1:01:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It emanates.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.11,1:01:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It emanates.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.11,1:01:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.25,1:01:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.86,1:01:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.65,1:01:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.65,1:01:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.71,1:01:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're feeling up here
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.38,1:01:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,between you and I,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.38,1:01:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that everyone's picking up out there
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.86,1:01:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,our love for each other
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.86,1:01:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone is seeing and picking up out there
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.86,1:02:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that vibration.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.05,1:02:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I share with everyone present
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.09,1:02:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I feel
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.92,1:02:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,within my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.53,1:02:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,every night when I go to bed
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.71,1:02:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank God
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.71,1:02:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for Susan's love every night.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.46,1:02:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you oh Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.76,1:02:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of your presence
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.76,1:02:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel God loves me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.05,1:02:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm surrounded by your love
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.05,1:02:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the kitty's love
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.05,1:02:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the doggy's love
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.05,1:02:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the love of all our friends.
